{"tid":1794032,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國女童 發現中國製聖誕卡有囚犯求救訊息","createTime":"2019-12-22T23:24:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T02:42:14.000Z","uid":134071,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f7a77e9473f332767069d99eaa9e1877ae2a7422","tid":1794032,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T23:24:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=374303&amp;refer=Share&amp;fbclid=IwAR1cLEmT5_pULWfromMPVmTZbB1IsBVQnt3SaiSlU4w6dNGP7YhEu8vlFVk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D374303%26refer%3DShare%26fbclid%3DIwAR1cLEmT5_pULWfromMPVmTZbB1IsBVQnt3SaiSlU4w6dNGP7YhEu8vlFVk&d=HJ1jiXHXfxJ2%2FxolOfbUwQ%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=430c1e95\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D374303%26refer%3DShare%26fbclid%3DIwAR1cLEmT5_pULWfromMPVmTZbB1IsBVQnt3SaiSlU4w6dNGP7YhEu8vlFVk&h=e2560f3b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=374303&amp;refer=Share&amp;fbclid=IwAR1cLEmT5_pULWfromMPVmTZbB1IsBVQnt3SaiSlU4w6dNGP7YhEu8vlFVk</a><br />\n<br />\n英女童發現中國製聖誕卡有囚犯求救訊息<br />\n7小時前<br />\n英女童發現中國製聖誕卡有囚犯求救訊息<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】英國一名女童購買中國製的慈善聖誕卡後，發現有人在其中一張卡上寫上求救訊息，聲稱上海青浦監獄是血汗工場。<br />\n<br />\n發現訊息的六歲女童是來自倫敦南部的維迪科姆，她早前在當地超市Tesco買了一盒聖誕卡後，發現其中一張已被人用過，並在卡上用英語寫下訊息，聲稱自己是上海青浦監獄的外國囚犯，又說他們被迫勞動，希望收到訊息的人幫助他們通知人權組織，和聯繫曾經同樣被囚禁在青浦監獄的英國前記者、前企業欺詐調查員漢弗萊。<br />\n<br />\nTesco發言人回應時說，對有關消息感到震驚，聲言公司討厭使用監獄勞工，宣布立即停止跟相關中國工廠合作並展開調查，超市亦會停售有關聖誕卡。"},{"pid":"2cd9ff28391dd18e47782e262d73d50c407987a6","tid":1794032,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T23:26:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad596e8a2c51cde95da85d0d54877d3d5a3e0657","tid":1794032,"uid":59898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T23:28:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5d4aa0603f6310abbc9b45cff2fa20c9a738ba5","tid":1794032,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T23:46:31.000Z","msg":"哩單要廣傳"},{"pid":"0de596d84c5f4de93071a6baaea40165fff58084","tid":1794032,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T23:51:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3720985c1194e7700258317a35ecc580b7ab4827","tid":1794032,"uid":13592,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T23:54:12.000Z","msg":"同華偉有粒backdoor晶片一樣 任佢砌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真又好假又好 時間最緊要啱啱好"},{"pid":"c2c98783a218306eec9f9e0f94db7e6b62563064","tid":1794032,"uid":29726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T00:04:42.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e4fca4fd04785db7e767cd38931de87c483fc00","tid":1794032,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T01:05:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"65b5595d5edaf8e31aff40da24de17465b36c615","tid":1794032,"uid":275477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T02:05:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f177c8b468019b469b087b331e8a6c5a2fe9801e","tid":1794032,"uid":193215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T02:31:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71532ecfbb866a594bf2e060aaf8e078c198b92b","tid":1794032,"uid":114781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T02:42:14.000Z","msg":"呢單英國而家著哂火<img src=\"/as